Rating: 4
These mashed potatoes were absolutely delicious. I served as part of my Thanksgiving meal and they were appreciated by all. I boil the potatoes and sauteed the mushrooms the day before, then before serving heated the milk/butter and mashed the potatoes. At the last minute, I added the mushrooms (warmed up slightly in the microwave). I used 1/2 cup of fresh, sliced green onion. Fantastic!

